    {
      "id": "PopularPost371164",
      "post_content": "If anyone's still confused about how to figure this card out, think of it this way:  \n  \nYou pay RR to summon one comet. You can spend more mana to adjust either the size of the comet (X) or to summon additional, equally large comets (multikicker).  \n  \ne.g. a size 5 comet with four targets costs RR (first comet) + 5 (size) + 3 (additional comets) = RR8.",
      "posted_by": "ZealousEntropy",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost371164\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">If anyone's still confused about how to figure this card out, think of it this way:<br/><br/>You pay RR to summon one comet. You can spend more mana to adjust either the size of the comet (X) or to summon additional, equally large comets (multikicker).<br/><br/>e.g. a size 5 comet with four targets costs RR (first comet) + 5 (size) + 3 (additional comets) = RR8.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '371164'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy65698\">ZealousEntropy</span>\r\n                                (4/19/2014 1:57:17 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Righ